{"tid":2334260,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"廣東大停電｜民眾無得上網沖涼突停水 內媒近12小時始報道：設備故障","createTime":"2020-12-21T05:14:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-21T05:48:57.000Z","uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d3e8487ed8d9253eaa2c5a3794667131c905c032","tid":2334260,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T05:14:31.000Z","msg":"大停電後，官方一直未有回應，故無法得知悉今次停電的範圍、受影響人數，廣東的媒體如《南方都巿報》、《廣州日報》今早一直未有相關的新聞。直至早上11時30分，《廣州日報》始在微博發帖：「12月21日凌晨0：00左右，因設備故障，影響廣州三元里、羅衝圍一帶部份用戶用電。記者從廣州供電局了解到，該公司立即組織緊急搶修，經過一個多小時的努力，恢復了全部受影響用戶供電。廣州電網目前運行穩定，電力供應平衡，無負荷缺口，不會拉閘限電。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201221/MF727BN4FZFVPPLDSSGHVW7CFQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201221%2FMF727BN4FZFVPPLDSSGHVW7CFQ%2F&d=Yr0hxYoWOJ9ZaoTMuy4WzIVlFhl8e2VpHQ9vpRm7Uxg%3D&h=b5cbde85\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201221%2FMF727BN4FZFVPPLDSSGHVW7CFQ%2F&h=4a993a57\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201221/MF727BN4FZFVPPLDSSGHVW7CFQ/</a>"},{"pid":"c0304d13f9762750d22cb3b957501176e1fd5c06","tid":2334260,"uid":142735,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T05:18:54.000Z","msg":"用左12小時諗原因，同埋點樣壓新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff70e1d669e6a003706c35aa4e68fab63e6285a3","tid":2334260,"uid":269864,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c0304d13f9762750d22cb3b957501176e1fd5c06","tid":2334260,"uid":142735,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T05:18:54.000Z","msg":"用左12小時諗原因，同埋點樣壓新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T05:26:49.000Z","msg":"其實搵尼d 解釋不如咩都唔講當冇事發生，反正都唔會有人信。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f48ad07f04c26233fd6ad4650e69e4186914c14","tid":2334260,"uid":14918,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"cited